com.datastax.oss.dsbulk.executor.reactor.reader

Interface ReactorBulkReader

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AutoCloseable, ReactiveBulkReader
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ReactorBulkExecutor
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ContinuousReactorBulkExecutor, DefaultReactorBulkExecutor

    public interface ReactorBulkReader
extends ReactiveBulkReader
    A reactive execution unit for bulk read operations using Reactor.

    Methods of this interface all return a Flux of read results.
